  "texts": [
    "This method requires no training data, and either minimal to no compute resources.Further, users can make use of prompt engineering [45] techniques to complete their task.",
    "Broadly, there are two main varieties of prompt engineering techniques i.e.",
    "zero-shot [46] and few-shot [47].",
    "In the case of zero-shot learning, Gen-AI techniques are able to perform the task at hand without seeing any prior examples, but just by leveraging the knowledge present in them.",
    "On the other hand in case of few-shot learning, users provide a few examples as part of the prompt for the Gen-AI techniques to learn and perform the task at the end of the prompt."
  ],
